        <title>「Hidden in plain sight： VLMs overlook their visual representations」の論文紹介</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/hidden-in-plain-sight-vlms-overlook-their-visual-representations%E3%81%AE%E8%AB%96%E6%96%87%E7%B4%B9%E4%BB%8B/</link>
